reviews.review_text: UVM.. oh the memories Boy oh boy.. I remember this show, and it was smoker. And yes, it really was a GYM! I remember all the spinners, spinning under and through the bleachers. Yep, there were bleachers!! Very nice recording, too. Thanks for uploading, and opening the floodgates of my misspent youth. :-)

I love your recordings Andrwe you do a GREAT job capturing the experience of the show live and in your face.  Thank you thank you thank you.
When I find the shows I was at and love as much as this one with a sound this good it puts a smile on my face for the day. Everyone already knows what made this show so hot so no need to comment on the songs them selves but get this one if dont have it yet
U OF V Ah jeeze, nice show, good recording, and its always nice to remember anything that happens in The Green Mountain State.
